Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:39.94,sign,,0,0,0,,MINUMAN TERBAIK TERSISA DI DASAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.79,sign,,0,0,0,,BISA SAYA BANTU?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:41.58,5-normal,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,69)\fs80\b1\bord4\c&H000008&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Kamiina Botan, Sosok Mabuknya Seindah Bunga Lili
